attr.title: LISA: The Timeless
attr.desc: LISA: The Timeless is a fangame set in the LISA universe made by Torrington. It's a story set outside of the main plot of the original LISA trilogy, based on the world established by Austin Jorgensen's title, LISA: The Painful.
attr.desc_md: LISA: The Timeless is a fangame set in the LISA universe made by Torrington. It's a story set outside of the main plot of the original LISA trilogy, based on the world established by Austin Jorgensen's title, LISA: The Painful.
attr.inst:
download the game from gamejolt,https://gamejolt.com/games/LISA-The-Timeless/629435 tested with Windows version. Copy all assets to the gamedata folder.

Note: This game is not ideal for devices with low resolution displays and/or absent joysticks.
